single-arg arrow:
  ((`=>` (X) ((`+` X 1))))
multi-arg arrow:
  ((`=>` ((X Y)) ((`+` X Y))))
  ((`=>` (X Y) ((`+` X Y))))
anonymous in call:
  (((`()` (`.` Xs map) (`=>` (X) ((`*` X X))))))
explicit function definition (`Name Args = Body`):
  ((`=` (f X) ((`+` X 1))))
  ((`=` (g X Y) ((`*` X Y))))
function with multi-line body via `|`:
  ((`=` (h X) ((`|` (Y (`*` X 2)) ((`+` Y 1))))))
method definition on a type via `T.`name:
  ((`=` ((`.` list double)) ((`()` (`.` Me map) (`=>` (X) ((`*` X 2)))))))
